Zambia’s Antitrust Authority Approves Copperbelt, Liquid Venture Agreement

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-07-01T07:54:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/zambia-s-antitrust-authority-approves-copperbelt-liquid-venture-agreement.html
Zambia’s antitrust authority approved
the proposed creation of a joint venture between Copperbelt
Energy Corp. and Liquid Telecommunications Holdings Ltd. of
Mauritius.  “The transaction did not raise competition concerns in the
fiber optic market,” the Competition and Consumer Protection
Commission of Zambia said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  